snippet.textDisplay:
It is suggested that the government follow the example of Taiwan to implement a strong national health insurance. National hospitals and pharmacies are controlled by the central government and a central health and welfare department is set up to take charge of the nation ’s health and health welfare affairs. It pays 10% of the basic health insurance premiums based on the deduction of each person's salary. The unpaid deduction or the 0.05% deduction from social welfare payments is automatically deducted from the computer to strive for fair and just treatment for health.
The central health authority has:
1. The Central Epidemic Prevention Office CDC controls the national epidemic command, dispatch, vaccine and pharmaceutical control and R & D production, national doctors and nursing staff human dispatch and epidemic prevention command, medical and medical material dispatch, setting, control, command, and disease control information, All doctors and nurses, pharmacists, and public health personnel in the country are in professional positions. They are in charge of controlling the harm of the disease, protecting the people of the country from fear, and indeed protecting the health of the people.
2. Establish a national food and medicine management office: in charge of controlling the import and export of the country and domestic food and medicine health, safety, use, transportation, distribution, scheduling, national food, medicine high-speed computer information, amendments and regulations.
3. Social Health Division: In charge of the control of the nation's people's health and social welfare, elderly health management, nursing homes for the elderly, child care homes, disability benefits, and the establishment of health medical premises.
4. National Health Law Office: responsible for the research, setting up, drafting, revising, and information management of the national people's health laws and regulations. It is held by the central government regulations personnel and national lawyers' public welfare organizations.
5. Taiwan has strong epidemic management capabilities and superior medical technology can cooperate with the United States to eliminate the covid19 virus together. There are many epidemic prevention experts in Taiwan to assist the government in various preparations for epidemic prevention.
May the Lord Jesus protect the people of the United States of America and God, and ask God to empower him to help President Trump and his people.
